<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. The pine forest (sapiniere) at Zonza, Samulaghia, in southern Corsica, investigated 24 - 28 June 2019 as part of the \" La Planete Revisitee Corsica 2019 \" survey." , "Figure 4. Female of Chelipoda puschae Ivkovic, Perovic & Grootaert, sp. nov." , "Figure 3. Male terminalia of Chelipoda puschae Ivkovic, Perovic & Grootaert, sp. nov. A ventral view B lateral view C lateral view D ventral view E dorsal view C-E show details of the apex. Abbreviations: Epan + Hypan, fused epandrium and hypandrium; lcer, lower lobe of cercus; ucer, upper lobe of cercus; subep, subepandrial process; ph, phallus. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 2. Male (not holotype) of Chelipoda puschae Ivkovic, Perovic & Grootaert, sp. nov." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/547254" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/547253" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/547252" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/547251" .

